name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Anthony JACKSON, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Anthony JACKSON, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 5th day of August, 2009, the Application for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of the entry of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

978 A.2d 348
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Anthony JACKSON, Petitioner.

Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
Aug. 5, 2009.
